### Health check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### Get items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items

### Get items with search, filter, sort, and pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items?search=mouse&category=Electronics&status=healthy&sortBy=quantity&order=desc&page=1&limit=8

### Get dashboard stats
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/stats/summary

### Create item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C Cable",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "quantity": 20,
  "price": 19.9,
  "reorderLevel": 5,
  "supplier": "Cable House",
  "notes": "1 meter cable"
}

### Update item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse Updated",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "quantity": 25,
  "price": 39.9,
  "reorderLevel": 8,
  "supplier": "TechZone Supplies",
  "notes": "Updated item"
}

### Delete item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/items/1
